Beerdora
========

Beer recommendation engine.

Sample usage:

    python get_beer_data.py    
    python make_training_data.py
    mono /path/to/ipy.exe recommend.py


Module descriptions:

config.py:
    Defines cross-module objects (e.g., constants).

get_beer_data.py:
    Reads recommendation data from a directory containing html documents with
    a consistent structure. Formats data and writes to database.

make_training_data.py:
    Reads data from database and outputs .csv files of training and test data.

recommend.py:
    CLI app to predict user beer ratings.

    
Notes: This program requires mono, ipython, and mymedialite.
